Detailed Description

Acts as a base class for FileBuilder & BuildCommand classes.

There is no use for BuildModel instances, this class is meant to be purely a base class for generalization.

bool BuildModel::replaceDefaultFlags_ [protected]

Specifies if the flags for generator are replaces of appended.

OPTIONAL spirit:replaceDefaultFlags When true, documents flags that replace any of the default flags from the build script generator. If false, the flags are appended.
